author: Alistair McGeorge
title: Kim Kardashian dines in New York as she fails to publicly congratulate Beyonce on pregnancy
text:
Showbiz Kim Kardashian dines in New York as she fails to publicly congratulate Beyonce on pregnancy The star appeared to be in good spirits on Wednesday - but there's still no sign of a message on social media Share   Thank you for subscribing!   
Kim Kardashian is yet to break her public silence and congratulate Beyonce on her recent pregnancy announcement. 
The star - who made a return to social media earlier this year after a break following her terrifying armed robbery in Paris back in October - was spotted out and about in New York City on Wednesday. 
Dressed in a long black fur coat to battle the cold weather and a pair of high heeled black boots, Kim - who went out for dinner with her pals including Jonathan Cheban - looked to be in great spirits. Kim is yet to publicly congratulate Beyonce (Photo: Splash News) She was spotted out for dinner in New York City (Photo: Splash News) 
She was seen walking through SoHo this week, on the same day fellow star Beyonce revealed she and Jay Z are expecting twins. 
Although Kim and her man Kanye West spent time with the couple last year, there have been constant rumours that they just don't get on . She hasn't referred to the happy news on social media (Photo: Splash News) 
It comes after Kanye blasted his former collaborator for not supporting him after Kim was robbed at gunpoint in Paris in an onstage rant at one of his Saint Pablo concerts. Beyonce, Jay Z, Kanye West and Kim Kardashian seen together back in 2012 (Photo: Getty) 
He fumed: "Don't call me, after the robbery, and say, 'How you feelin?' You wanna know how I'm feelin? Come by the house. 
"Bring the kids by the house like we're brothers. Let's sit down. I can't take this s**t bro. Our kids have never even played together." Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
